Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:26.92,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:30.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:33.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:48.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:55.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:01:02.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:10.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:13.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:17.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:21.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:24.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.48,0:01:28.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:32.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:35.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:39.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:43.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:46.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:49.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:55.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:01:58.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's trying to defy the Franky Family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the money back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Give me the money back"? Then are\Nyou one of the Straw Hat's underlings?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Bro! Since he's with\NStraw Hat Luffy, I expected him to be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a really strong pirate, but then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll admit you've got guts to come\Nto get the money back all by yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't let you have it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to... have our ship repaired...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That money is crucial to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that money, we can finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can finally repair the Merry's scars!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you jerks have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:40.11,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Rescuing Our Friend!\NRaid on the Franky House"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so worked up about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you love your ship quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no matter what happens to your ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this money is already ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately for you, no matter what we\Nsteal from pirates, we won't be accused
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of committing a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is dirty money that you stole\Nfrom somewhere anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let us have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like, try begging the Navy for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are the ones who'll be captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for Straw Hat Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that he has a useless underling\Nwho can't even watch over money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, have some fun with him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take this money\Nand go shopping at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is gonna be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Special Attack! Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember this, long-nosed boy.\NMy name is Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to leave this town alive,\Nyou shouldn't cross me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... What're you doing?! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a pathetic weapon wouldn't work on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, Long-nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the 200 million Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back to me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it... back to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Give it back to me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it... back to me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to hold out until Robin comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll only become a burden to\Nthem if I march in with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be scary, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, I'll protect this ship and\Nthe 100 million Berries all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you... guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop. Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember right, this should be\Nthe place Nami-san was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. This is the backstreet shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go up this canal... and here!\NUsopp is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Nami-san, where can we find these\Ndemolition workers, the Franky Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure? Didn't you just\Nscrew up the directions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not you! Keep your mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What'd you say?!\N--Ah, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot! He just walked off\Nwithout waiting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:04.04,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ahhh..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!\NWhere'd you come falling from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shipyard...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was jumping around imitating this\None shipwright to look for Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. We've got a problem, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp got abducted along with the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. We're on our way to their hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp got beaten up and had\Nthe money stolen from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that he felt responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and went to pick a fight with\Nthe Franky Family all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then... I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what a stubborn man he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we don't know\Nwhether he has it or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they send me out this far each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish people would put themselves in my shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kalifa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be worn out, Iceberg-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have some tea today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've prepared it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Just as I'd expect from you, Kalifa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Corgy is always angry\Nwhen he leaves, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth does he come to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants something I have,\Nso he suggests all sorts of deals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be something very precious, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I always tell him that I don't know\Nwhat he's talking about and refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They really are a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he breathing, Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although he's completely\Nunconscious, he's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be okay. I can save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a bit... Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go blow that stupid house away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Go get more food!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got money!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The alcohol today sure tastes good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've drawn graffiti on the walls of\Npeople's houses for all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! So you took my goggles back from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you a story about when I bravely\Nfought Sea Kings in the Calm Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big ones! They were...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-And what's more...\NI have 8,000 men under me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That large amount of money... They stole it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't face everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you beat up every one of them, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you wanna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? You lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go buy some food!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you buy all the food at\Nthe store, okay?! We've got money!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit. Just you wait and see.\NI'll beat you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you jerks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you came to get the\Nmoney back, huh, you fools?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See all the guys here? What do\Nyou think the four of you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, well... you're here.\NYou've got a bounty on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't you leave\Nthat head of yours with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the captain of that weak long-nosed guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't be that strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, shorty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's punching? At that huge steel armor\Nthat even a battleship cannon can't shatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're just fooling around,\NI'll go ahead and crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He punched a hole in that huge armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a sec, you guys! Let's have a talk first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's... Let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fire cannonballs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Raven...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The cannonballs are made of iron, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a cannon, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad news! These guys are seriously bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Get out of here!\NGet out through the back door!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You started the fight. Don't act pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Party Table...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kick Course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We can't use the back door!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Windows! Get out through the windows!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumble...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Horn Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roseo Colonnade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wait a sec, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The money, right?!\NYou want the money back, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 200 million Berries that\Nworthless guy had, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, that money is no longer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our boss, Franky, took that\Nmoney and went shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he's buying something\Non the black market,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we don't know where he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, no matter how much\Nyou go on a rampage here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that 200 million Berries won't come ba--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a goner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Zambai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:19:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough out of you.\NIt has nothing to do with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll beat you up so bad that\Nnot even your bones will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even our bones?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Don't get frightened!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Not even your bones will remain"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is what we, the Franky Family,\Ndemolition workers and bounty hunters, say!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show them the Franky House's specialty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything Shot Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come! Attack them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't flinch! Keep firing\Nuntil we run out of cannonballs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only four of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're those noises? Fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from the northeast! They're coming\Nfrom the direction of the Franky House!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Them again? What's the fuss about this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yea... Ugh! Shh! He'll hear us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy, they're getting too carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They really don't show any\Nrestraint when they party, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay once in a while, right?\NIt's a wonderful day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go follow Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drat. Looks like they really\Ndon't know where the money is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we strangle this Franky guy,\Nif he already spent the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do now? Even if we wait for\Nhim here, he won't be back for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I finished giving him first aid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to take him on a stretcher,\Nso help me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Staying here talking won't get us anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to the ship for now.\NWe left Nami-san alone there, too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have the thing with\NRobin-chan to deal with...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the issues with the ship, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's say goodbye... to the Going Merry here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:23.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:26.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:32.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:34.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:37.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:43.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:46.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:49.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:51.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:54.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:57.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:00.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:06.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:09.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:11.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:14.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.41,0:23:19.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, you're taking the joke too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.59,0:23:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll say goodbye to the Merry here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.84,0:23:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bull! Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.84,0:23:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship can't be fixed anymore!\NShe'll sink soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--No matter what you say,\NI'm never gonna give up on Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.44,0:23:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Big Fight under the Moon!\NThe Pirate Flag Flutters with Sorrow!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
